    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219110/extras/d01d7bc736367eb6b0c3c9c499df21c5.apng?t=1766920400\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219110/extras/d01d7bc736367eb6b0c3c9c499df21c5.poster.avif?t=1766920400\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=250 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the size-changing Globs in this colorful puzzle game. Use the curious properties of their bodies at your advantage to solve a variety of levels, by using them to push each other or against walls, squeeze into tight gaps, grow to block holes, and many more surprises, all in a lively and expressive pixel art aesthetic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The puzzles are designed to be approachable, but provide additional optional challenges for players wishing to put their puzzle-solving skills to the test. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 40 levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A jazzy and upbeat soundtrack </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Expressive character animations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Four different themed worlds each with an unique visual identity</p></li></ul>",
